{
  "stem": "4963.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunt and uncle did well financially, I mean, according to their-- to the standards.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because he was a-- you know, he immediately got fees for his medical practice and my aunt for dental.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw everything, but I-- I couldn't-- you know, I knew how to-- how to keep quiet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And God forbid that anybody would find out that my parents were sent to Siberia, because then I would be a prisoner as well.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, then this went on for a year, and conditions were very bad all around us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Again, I was pretty lucky-- I sometimes say that I was born with a lucky star above me-- that no matter under the circumstances I still, you know, had it relatively good.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we had enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had some clothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, now-- of course, one dress, you know, a pair of shoes, maybe some-- something to change into something else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of leftovers from-- you know, from one because my cousin also lived with us and she was two years younger than I was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- however, I don't remember ever really bemoaning the fact that I-- because we were all in the same situation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing that I remember really of-- I was very sick at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I lived at home, I had every disease you can think of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nothing that-- that was really outstanding that I-- I can think of while I was with my aunt and uncle-- a cold here and there, but not much otherwise.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember many fillings in my teeth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My aunt would always fill it for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, then the rumors went around that the Aliyah Bet was quite active in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
